title: Spyforce - 05 - The Bridge (1971).avi
description:
In an attempt to stop Colonel Cato from sending them on a dangerous mission to Papua New Guinea, Erskine and Adolf get themselves arrested for a petty crime.

The sentencing judge however, is Col. Cato!

He sentences them to "3 months gaol with hard labour" - Erskine and Adolf think they've foiled Cato's plan to send them to PNG.

How wrong could they be ?
